Yeah, when did he leave?

305
00:13:50,817 --> 00:13:53,184
Yeah, that's rude.

306
00:13:55,850 --> 00:13:57,749
You know, it's nice
to spend time with people

307
00:13:57,803 --> 00:14:01,026
who don't talk about work like
it's some kind of soap opera.

308
00:14:01,263 --> 00:14:04,197
Jennifer still trying
to sleep her way to the top?

309
00:14:06,130 --> 00:14:07,975
Yeah.

310
00:14:08,702 --> 00:14:11,335
You should be happy someone
wants to do the stuff with Penny

311
00:14:11,396 --> 00:14:12,561
you don't want to.

312
00:14:12,678 --> 00:14:14,318
Yeah, I wish I had that
with Howard.

313
00:14:14,365 --> 00:14:15,374
Wait.

314
00:14:15,934 --> 00:14:17,418
What? What do I make you do?

315
00:14:17,663 --> 00:14:19,271
Let's see:
the magic store,

316
00:14:19,394 --> 00:14:21,154
the Doctor Who convention,

317
00:14:21,240 --> 00:14:24,663
the National Belt Buckle
Collector's meet and greet.

318
00:14:25,779 --> 00:14:27,226
