on the invitation,

319
00:14:27,250 --> 00:14:28,302
"Buckle up for fun."

320
00:14:28,327 --> 00:14:30,341
It's not my fault
you didn't listen.

321
00:14:32,249 --> 00:14:34,058
I'm sure I'm overreacting.

322
00:14:34,202 --> 00:14:36,044
You're entitled
to feel how you feel.

323
00:14:36,124 --> 00:14:38,178
If you don't like it,
you should just talk to her.

324
00:14:38,255 --> 00:14:40,561
